---
import { getCompanyInfo } from "../../lib/api";
const company = await getCompanyInfo("AGE");
const legalEmail = company?.supportEmail ?? company?.primaryEmail ?? null;
---
<div class="px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto pb-24 space-y-24 md:space-y-32">

  <!-- Terms of Service -->
  <section id="tos" class="scroll-mt-32">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl text-[#041632] md:sticky md:top-40">
          Terms of<br class="hidden md:block" /> Service
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3 space-y-6 text-[#44474d] leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-lg text-[#191c1d] font-medium">
          By accessing the Amrita Global Enterprises (AGE) platform, you agree to abide by the following terms of manufacturing and supply engagement.
        </p>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl text-[#041632] italic mt-8 mb-3">1. General Engagement</h3>
          <p>AGE provides textile manufacturing services and wholesale product distribution globally. These terms govern all transactions made through our digital portal or via direct procurement contracts.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl text-[#041632] italic mt-8 mb-3">2. Intellectual Property</h3>
          <p>All designs, loom patterns, and textile specifications provided by AGE remain the proprietary intellectual property of Amrita Global Enterprises unless explicitly transferred via a signed Intellectual Property Assignment agreement.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl text-[#041632] italic mt-8 mb-3">3. Limitation of Liability</h3>
          <p>While we strive for technical perfection, AGE is not liable for indirect or consequential losses resulting from shipping delays beyond our control or fluctuations in raw material quality provided by third-party suppliers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy Policy -->
  <section id="privacy" class="scroll-mt-32 bg-[#f3f4f5] p-8 md:p-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl text-[#041632]">
          Privacy<br class="hidden md:block" /> Policy
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3 space-y-6 text-[#44474d] leading-relaxed">
        <p>Your data security is paramount in our global operations. We collect data solely to facilitate international trade and improve logistics.</p>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl text-[#041632] italic mt-8 mb-3">Data Collection</h3>
          <p>We collect business identifiers, including corporate tax IDs, shipping coordinates, and procurement history. We do not sell this data to marketing firms.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl text-[#041632] italic mt-8 mb-3">Security Standards</h3>
          <p>All transactional data is encrypted using industry-standard protocols. Access is restricted to authorized logistics and account management personnel.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cookie Policy -->
  <section id="cookies" class="scroll-mt-32 border-l-4 border-[#fed488] pl-8 md:pl-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl text-[#041632]">
          Cookie<br class="hidden md:block" /> Policy
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3 space-y-6 text-[#44474d] leading-relaxed">
        <p>Our platform uses "Essential Cookies" to maintain session integrity during high-volume wholesale ordering.</p>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl text-[#041632] italic mt-8 mb-3">Functional Cookies</h3>
          <p>These allow our system to remember your technical specifications and preferred fabric catalogs across different browsing sessions.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl text-[#041632] italic mt-8 mb-3">Analytics</h3>
          <p>We use anonymized telemetry to understand which loom technologies and textile categories are garnering international interest to better scale our production facilities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Wholesale Rules -->
  <section id="wholesale" class="scroll-mt-32">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl text-[#041632]">
          Wholesale<br class="hidden md:block" /> Rules
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3">
        <div class="bg-white border-t-2 border-[#775a19] p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-[#775a19] shrink-0"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 12h-4c0 1.66-1.34 3-3 3s-3-1.34-3-3H5V5h14v10z"/></svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-label font-bold text-[#041632] uppercase text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">
                Minimum Order Quantities (MOQ)
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#44474d] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Standard production runs require a minimum of 500 meters per colorway or 200 units for finished garments, unless otherwise specified in the technical data sheet.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-[#775a19] shrink-0"><path d="M20 4H4c-1.11 0-1.99.89-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.11.89 2 2 2h16c1.11 0 2-.89 2-2V6c0-1.11-.89-2-2-2zm0 14H4v-6h16v6zm0-10H4V6h16v2z"/></svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-label font-bold text-[#041632] uppercase text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">
                Payment Milestones
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#44474d] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                50% upfront deposit is required to initiate raw material procurement. The remaining 50% is due upon Bill of Lading (BOL) generation for international shipments.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-[#775a19] shrink-0"><path d="M23 12l-2.44-2.79.34-3.69-3.61-.82-1.89-3.2L12 2.96 8.6 1.5 6.71 4.69 3.1 5.5l.34 3.7L1 12l2.44 2.79-.34 3.7 3.61.82 1.89 3.2L12 21.04l3.4 1.46 1.89-3.19 3.61-.82-.34-3.69L23 12zm-12.91 4.72l-3.8-3.81 1.48-1.48 2.32 2.33 5.85-5.87 1.48 1.48-7.33 7.35z"/></svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-label font-bold text-[#041632] uppercase text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">
                Quality Inspection
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[#44474d] text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Clients are entitled to a 72-hour inspection window post-delivery. Any variance from the master sample must be reported within this period for remedial action.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Legal Contact -->
  <footer class="pt-8 border-t border-[#c5c6ce]/30 text-center">
    <a
      href={legalEmail ? `mailto:${legalEmail}` : "/support"}
      class="inline-flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-[#041632] text-white hover:bg-[#775a19] transition-all"
    >
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20 7H9.83L7.83 5H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V9c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-5 8H9v-2h6v2zm2-4H7v-2h10v2z"/></svg>
      <span class="font-label text-sm font-medium">
        {legalEmail ? <>For legal inquiries, contact <span class="font-bold underline">{legalEmail}</span></> : "Contact our legal team"}
      </span>
    </a>
    <p class="mt-8 text-[#44474d] text-xs font-label uppercase tracking-widest">
      Amrita Global Enterprises &bull; Compliance Division
    </p>
  </footer>

</div>
